      <title>债券交易商期待拍卖创纪录，标志着 5% 收益率已达峰值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/bond-traders-look-to-record-auction-for-sign-5-yield-is-peak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国国债有望迎来今年最糟糕的一个月，大量拍卖即将到来，这是对收益率在达到 2024 年最高水平后是否已见顶的重大考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/bond-traders-look-to-record-auction-for-sign-5-yield-is-peak</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
